Job Responsibilities

Responsible for IT helpdesk work, quickly responding and dealing with user desktop problems and needs;
Responsible for the daily maintenance of IT desktops and related equipment, including PCs, printers, scanners, electronic scales, and other equipment and related software maintenance;
Responsible for the installation and distribution of IT desktop related equipment and systems;
Responsible for the security and stability of the IT network (including wireless network) environment;
Responsible for the management and maintenance of CCTV monitoring equipment;
Assist the asset department in managing and updating assets. Including asset warehousing, issuance, inventory, maintenance, and scrap management.

Requirements

Computer-related major, with practical related work experience;
Possess strong problem analysis and solving skills, high sense of responsibility, good professional ethics, a strong sense of service, and proactive;
Proficient in Windows, macOS, and other operating systems, proficient in the installation and troubleshooting of office software and common software;
Skilled in solving the faults of terminal equipment such as PCs, printers, telephones, scanners, electronic scales, etc.;
Master the configuration, use, and policy formulation of mainstream VPN, online behavior management, access, firewall, and other security equipment;
Master the configuration, maintenance, fault diagnosis, and optimization of routers, switches, WLCs, APs, and other network equipment;
Master the basic use and maintenance of CCTV monitoring equipment;
Understand enterprise IT infrastructure, and have a certain understanding of weak current integrated wiring, servers, virtualization, etc.

Interested Parties please feel free to click the button above for APPLYING/ WhatsApp / call 6603 4144

崗位職責

負責IThelpdesk工作，快速相應和處理用戶桌面端問題和需求；
負責IT桌面及相關設備的日常維護工作，包括PC、打印機、掃描儀、電子秤等設備及相關軟件維護；
負責IT桌面相關設備和系統的安裝、配發工作；
負責IT網絡（包含無線網絡）環境安全穩定；
負責CCTV監控設備管理、維護工作；
協助資產部門進行資產的管理與更新。包括資產入庫、發放、盤點、維修、報廢管理。

入職要求

計算機相關專業，具有實際相關工作經驗；
具備較強的問題分析和解決能力，高度責任感，良好的職業道德，服務意識強，積極進取；
熟練掌握Windows、MacOS等操作系統相關知識，熟練office辦公軟件及常用軟件的安裝和故障解決；
熟練解決PC機、打印機、電話、掃描儀、電子秤等終端設備的故障；
掌握主流VPN、上網行為管理、准入、防火牆等安全設備的配置、使用及策略的製定；
掌握路由器、交換機、WLC、AP等網絡設備的配置、維護、故障診斷及優化；
掌握CCTV監控設備的基本使用和維護；
了解企業IT基礎架構，對弱電綜合佈線、服務器、虛擬化等方面有一定認識。

有意者請隨時點擊上方按鈕申請/whatsapp/致電6603 4144
